title: Hitrecord on TV S01E06 games
description: "HitRECord on TV" -- HitRECord is an online production company and website founded by Golden Globe-nominated actor Joseph Gordon-Levitt that features projects from artists around the world who submit their work to the site. The site has now morphed into this half-hour series, hosted by Gordon-Levitt, that features work from the same global online community that provides content on the site. Each episode features a theme that the included short films, music and other forms of art are based around. Episode themes include fantasy, trash, space and money.
